<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>balls</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta property=og:type content="website">
    <meta property=og:url content="https://balls.leadrdrk.eu.org/">
    <meta property=og:title content="balls">
    <meta property=og:description content="commands">
    <meta property=og:image content="https://balls.leadrdrk.eu.org/balls.png">
    <meta name="title" content="balls">
    <meta name="description" content="commands">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.8.1/css/bulma.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.13.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha256-h20CPZ0QyXlBuAw7A+KluUYx/3pK+c7lYEpqLTlxjYQ=" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="common.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/js-cookie@2/src/js.cookie.min.js"></script>
    <script src="common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="main" class="hero is-fullheight is-dark">
        <div class="hero-head">
            <nav id="navbar" class="bd-navbar navbar navbar-spacing is-dark">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="navbar-brand">
                        <div class="navbar-item">
                            <img src="balls.png" style="max-height: 3rem;"></img>
                            <a class="brand-name" href="/">balls</a>
                            <a class="navbar-item is-hidden-desktop" onclick="toggleDarkMode()" title="Toggle dark mode"><i class="fas fa-moon"></i></a>
                        </div>
                        <a role="button" class="navbar-burger" aria-label="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-target="navMenu" style="width: 4rem; height: 4rem">
                            <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="navMenu" class="navbar-menu">
                        <div class="navbar-end">
                            <a class="navbar-item" href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i>Home</a>
                            <a class="navbar-item" href="/commands"><i class="fas fa-list"></i>Commands</a>
                            <a class="navbar-item" href="/changelog"><i class="fas fa-sticky-note"></i>Changelog</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-body" style="display: block;">
            <section class="section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3 class="title">Commands</h3>
                    <b>Prefix:</b> <code>-</code><br>
                    <br>
                    Arguments in &lt;these quotes&gt; are required.<br>
                    Arguments in [these quotes] are optional.<br>
                    <br>
                    <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
                        <table class="table has-background-black-bis has-text-white">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="has-text-grey-lighter" style="text-align:left">Command</th>
                                    <th class="has-text-grey-lighter" style="text-align:left">Usage</th>
                                    <th class="has-text-grey-lighter" style="text-align:left">Description</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                            <% for (var command in helpContent) { %>
                                <% var item = helpContent[command]; %> 
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <%= command %>
                                        <% if (item.experimental) { %>
                                            <b><sup style="color: red;">[EXPERIMENTAL]</sup></b>
                                        <% }; %>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <%= item.usage.replace("<input>", "") %>
                                        <% if (item.usage.includes("<input>")) { %>
                                            <a href="#input">&lt;input&gt;</a>
                                        <% }; %>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <%- item.desc %>
                                        <% if (item.aliases) { %>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>Aliases: </b><%= item.aliases.join(", ") %>
                                        <% }; %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            <% }; %>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="section">
                <div class="container">
                    <h3 class="title" id="input">Input</h3>
                    What can you use as an input ?<br>
                    <br>
                    You can <b>attach a file</b>, or <b>include an url</b> to the file in your message. You can also
                    <b>ping a user</b> or <b>include their user id</b> to use their avatar as an input. Or you can provide
                    nothing and the bot will use the most recent file as input.<br>
                    <br>
                    All input files are limited to 12MiB in size (regardless if you have Nitro or not)
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
        <div id="footer" class="hero-foot">
            <div class="container is-spaced has-text-white has-text-centered">
                <span class="footer-text">another fine product by</span> 
                <a href="https://leadrdrk.eu.org/">
                    <img src="https://files.leadrdrk.eu.org/assets/logo.png" class="footer-logo"></img>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
